quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  14,7,Wa 'Idh Ta'adhana Rabbukum La'in Shakartum La'azīdannakum Wa La'in Kafartum 'Inna `Adhābī Lashadīdun
  14,8,Wa Qāla Mūsá 'In Takfurū 'Antum Wa Man Fī Al-'Arđi Jamī`āan Fa'inna Allāha Laghanīyun Ĥamīdun
  14,9,Alam Ya'tikum Naba'u Al-Ladhīna Min Qablikum Qawmi Nūĥin Wa `Ādin Wa Thamūda Wa Al-Ladhīna Min Ba`dihim Lā Ya`lamuhum 'Illā Allāhu Jā'at/hum Rusuluhum Bil-Bayyināti Faraddū 'Aydiyahum Fī 'Afwāhihim Wa Qālū 'Innā Kafarnā Bimā 'Ursiltum Bihi Wa 'Innā Lafī Shakkin Mimmā Tad`ūnanā 'Ilayhi Murībin
  14,10,Qālat Rusuluhum 'Afī Allāhi Shakkun Fāţiri As-Samāwāti Wa Al-'Arđi Yad`ūkum Liyaghfira Lakum Min Dhunūbikum Wa Yu'uakhkhirakum 'Ilá 'Ajalin Musammáan Qālū 'In 'Antum 'Illā Basharun Mithlunā Turīdūna 'An Taşuddūnā `Ammā Kāna Ya`budu 'Ābā'uunā Fa'tūnā Bisulţānin Mubīnin
  14,11,Qālat Lahum Rusuluhum 'In Naĥnu 'Illā Basharun Mithlukum Wa Lakinna Allāha Yamunnu `Alá Man Yashā'u Min `Ibādihi Wa Mā Kāna Lanā 'An Na'tiyakum Bisulţānin 'Illā Bi'idhni Allāhi Wa `Alá Allāhi Falyatawakkali Al-Mu'uminūna
  14,12,Wa Mā Lanā 'Allā Natawakkala `Alá Allāhi Wa Qad Hadānā Subulanā Wa Lanaşbiranna `Alá Mā 'Ādhaytumūnā Wa `Alá Allāhi Falyatawakkali Al-Mutawakkilūna